Package frc.robot.BreakerLib.util.test.selftest

Class SelfTest

java.lang.Object
edu.wpi.first.wpilibj2.command.SubsystemBase
frc.robot.BreakerLib.util.test.selftest.SelfTest
All Implemented Interfaces:
edu.wpi.first.util.sendable.Sendable, edu.wpi.first.wpilibj2.command.Subsystem
public class SelfTest
extends edu.wpi.first.wpilibj2.command.SubsystemBase
Core class of BreakerLib's SelfTest fuctionality, handling periodic passive (unless user configured otherwise) diagnostic self tests of all manually or automatically regeistered BreakerSelfTestable compatible devices, or devices registered through an instance of the SystemDiagnostics class.
